 Cloud vs Hybrid Device Management
Intended for cloud-first or cloud-only organizations.

Devices can be:

Entra ID Joined (cloud-only)

Hybrid Joined (cloud + on-prem)

Why Hybrid Join?
Legacy Win32 apps cannot migrate to the cloud.

Entra ID does not support Group Policies (GPOs).

On-prem admins can still manage devices using GPOs.

 Hybrid Join - Additional Notes
Hybrid join is useful when admins need to manage different OS images on-prem.

Works best for OS versions:

Windows 8.1 → Windows 11

 Group Policy Objects (GPOs)
What are GPOs?
Centralized collections of configuration & security settings in on-prem Active Directory.

Why GPOs don’t work in Entra ID
GPOs require:

Domain Controllers

LDAP

SYSVOL

Microsoft Entra ID is cloud-native, built on:

REST APIs

Web protocols

Therefore, GPOs cannot exist in Entra ID.

